d7b4a854a11f5da785941066a046c563ad23b37","tid":2033851,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f9d7e2f02365a1e6eae127028f1b436726f867","tid":2033851,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"劉曉明促英方客觀公正看待香港國安法<br />\n25.05.2020 08:24<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英國大使劉曉明接受央視訪問，指英方自本港去年修例風波以來，有些做法干涉香港內部事務，損害中英關係，要求英方準確理解香港國安法的內容，客觀公正看待，尊重中方的立場和關切，以及中國的核心利益，停止干涉香港事務，多做有利於香港繁榮穩定、有利於中英關係的事。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明又指，如果沒有外部勢力插手和干涉香港修例風波，局勢絕不會發展到如此嚴峻地步，目前已到了必須制止的時候，全國人大決定為香港訂立國安法，是堵住香港國家安全的風險漏洞，亦為中方在外交戰線維護國家安全，增添底氣和信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289895&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289895%26csid%3D261_367&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d6f774f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289895&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"兩步share文宣大法！㩒兩個制都唔肯㩒你仲係咪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入去個website揀張圖 㩒share去whatsapp 就可以send哂俾親戚朋友同各大群組<br />\n都可以share上Facebook同twitter！<br />\n<br />\n全民文宣呀！！！ Share27號國歌法二讀同埋國安法嘅文宣出去呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://swallowlife.org/lennon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fswallowlife.org%2Flennon&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=8bc186fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://swallowlife.org/lennon</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuSDR0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuSDR0K.png&h=6720a9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主幫手置頂得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1917ae53067896e7b1d4708f24dab293705bedc2","tid":2033851,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1dffdbe2759cece830054bccb7daf39e80ed14fd","tid"